metrics_conclusion: In terms of chords and melody, Forgiveness is significantly more complex than the typical song, having above average scores in Chord Complexity, Melodic Complexity, Chord-Melody Tension, Chord Progression Novelty and Chord-Bass Melody.
key_conclusion: Forgiveness has sections analyzed in the following keys: D Major,  and D Mixolydian.  Click on the linked cheat sheets for popular chords, chord progressions, downloadable midi files and more!

metadata.editComments: Chord progression mirrors the lyrics beautifully!
"Running in circles" is a great description of the chord progression.
"I'm still looking for that highway / Wondering if I went the wrong way / But I ain't lost...". Indeed, so many different (musical )ways to get to the destination...
